        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Movie Rental. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.</p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your name, email address, phone number, and age when you register an account.</li>
            <li>Rental history and preferences for movies.</li>
            <li>Payment details for transactions (processed securely by third-party payment providers).</li>
            <li>Technical data such as IP address, browser type, and access times.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your data for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and manage movie rental services.</li>
            <li>To personalize your experience and recommend movies.</li>
            <li>To process payments and manage transactions.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you regarding updates, promotions, or support inquiries.</li>
            <li>To enhance security and prevent fraud.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Protection and Security</h2>
        <p>We implement security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no online platform is 100% secure, and we advise users to keep their login details confidential.</p>

        <h2>5. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or trade your personal information. However, we may share your data with:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Trusted third-party services for payment processing and security.</li>
            <li>Legal authorities if required by law.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience. You can manage your cookie settings in your browser.</p>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access or request a copy of your personal data.</li>
            <li>Request data correction or deletion.</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We encourage you to review it periodically.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <strong>support@movierental.com</strong>.</p>

        
